    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is in stunning, showroom-ready shape! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. It\u2019s honestly the cleanest ride you\u2019ll find out there. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
