    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade example of the A80 platform, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six powerplant. This unit retains its factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering linear power through a crisp Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission. The chassis integrity is absolute, maintaining original torsional rigidity with zero modifications to the double-wishbone suspension or subframe mounting points. Every mechanical component, from the limited-slip differential to the four-piston braking calipers, operates with factory-new precision. This is a rare, numbers-matching specimen for the discerning collector who values mechanical purity and engineering excellence.",
