    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standards and presented in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, reflecting a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains factory-fresh; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every surface is free of scuffs or aging. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity audio system to the climate control, function with out-of-the-box precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio that documents its meticulous upkeep. It delivers a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer seeking an investment-grade example that requires absolutely no reconditioning, this is the definitive choice.",
