      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the E46 chassis. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014eliminating the primary failure points of this platform. The limited-slip differential and suspension bushings remain in factory-spec tolerance, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no swirl marks or oxidation. This is a turn-key enthusiast example with a documented service history and zero deferred maintenance.",
